        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>IRS Customer Service and Modernization Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Internal Revenue Service to (1) develop a written corrective action plan to improve tax return processing times, and (2) adopt measures to improve communication with the public.</p>]]>
        </text>
